<CONTENT id="_3793159_1"><TITLE value="Presentation"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;p&gt;This is the presentation for Session 8&lt;/p&gt;&#xd;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-43740565_1" alt="" width="125" height="101" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xd;
&lt;p&gt;After you finish the presentations please explore the Mitre ATT&amp;amp;CK starting with the tour&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://attack.mitre.org/matrices/enterprise/?tour=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Matrix - Enterprise | MITRE ATT&amp;amp;CK®&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Don't just click &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;next &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;then &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;next &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;without spending a minute or so looking around each page to see what information it presents and its layout.&lt;br&gt;The tour ends at the versions page, but on that page there are plenty more links to explore.&lt;/p&gt;&#xd;
&lt;p&gt;Lastly, Known attackers have been organized into groups including their history of attacks and the techniques they use. &lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://attack.mitre.org/groups/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Groups | MITRE ATT&amp;amp;CK®&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
